      <title>耶伦表示商业地产令人担忧，但监管机构正在关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/yellen-says-commercial-property-is-a-worry-regulators-are-on-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，虽然商业房地产的损失令人担忧，但美国监管机构正在努力确保金融体系的贷款损失准备金和流动性水平足以应对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/yellen-says-commercial-property-is-a-worry-regulators-are-on-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:29:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
